{"lemma":"دَعْوَى","slug":"دَعْوَى","root":"د.ع.#","root_slug":"د-ع-_","root_link":"/words/roots/د-ع-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"دَعْوَى","root":"دعو","pos":"N","occurrence_count":4},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n12621"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AF%D9%8E%D8%B9%D9%92%D9%88%D9%8E%D9%89"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"assertion"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"claim"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"lawsuit, process"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"legal title"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/daʕ.waː/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n12621","headword_ar":"دَعْوَى","root":"dEw","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"duEaA='N","text_ar":"دُعَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in five places. ―         -b2-  Also a subst. from 8; (S, M, Mgh, Msb, TA;) omitted in the K, though better known than the sun; (TA;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daEaAwapN","text_ar":"دَعَاوَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"diEaAwapN","text_ar":"دِعَاوَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"diEowapN","text_ar":"دِعْوَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) accord. to the general pronunciation, (M, TA,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daEowapN","text_ar":"دَعْوَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) accord. to the pronunciation of 'Adee of Er-Rabáb, (M, TA,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAEiyapN","text_ar":"دَاعِيَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA, there said to be syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daEowaY","text_ar":"دَعْوَى"},{"kind":"text","text":";) [meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An assertion that a thing belongs to one,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is due to one; a claim;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as is indicated in the S and Mgh and K &c.;]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a demand; a suit;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Yz, Az, Msb;) whether true"},{"kind":"page_break","n":885},{"kind":"text","text":"or false: (Mgh, K, TA:) the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daEowaY","text_ar":"دَعْوَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daEaAwK","text_ar":"دَعَاوٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daEaAwaY","text_ar":"دَعَاوَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"; the former of which is preferable accord. to some, being, as IJ says, the original form; but some say that the latter is preferable: (Msb:) [the latter only is mentioned in the Mgh:] the alif in the sing. [written"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":"] is a sign of the fem. gender; and therefore the word is without tenween. (Mgh.) Yz mentions the sayings,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liY fiY h`*aA AlA^amori daEowaY","text_ar":"لِى فِى هٰذَا الاَمْرِ دَعْوَى"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I have, in respect of this thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a claim"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a demand,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daEaAwaY","text_ar":"دَعَاوَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daEaAwK","text_ar":"دَعَاوٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"claims"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"demands,"},{"kind":"text","text":"as written in different copies. (Az, Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lawo A^uEoTiYa Aln~aAsu","text_ar":"لَوْ اُعْطِىَ النَّاسُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bidaEaAwiyhimo","text_ar":"بِدَعَاوِيهِمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"If men were given according to their claims,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"demands,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] occurs in a trad. (Msb.) ―         -b3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"diEowapN","text_ar":"دِعْوَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["M","Msb","K","TA","Mgh"]}]}}